projects.title: Ride Share Application for College Students
projects.description: A useful Ride Share Android Mobile Application for Students of Graphic Era University, they can use it to find Common commute to and fro College.

projects.title: Recipies From Frige
projects.description: No more Hassle in Searching For what to cook with what's in fridge! A simple Web application for finding Recipies that can be made with available ingredients

projects.title: University Management System
projects.description: A Full Stack University management System made in Core java. Which is used to perform the daily management tasks of a university. As Well as acts as an ERP system for Students. MySql used for Database

projects.title: Nano OS
projects.description: A bootable shell based Operating System with File System Functionalaties and upto 10 file system commands. Used for Educational purposes. Can be booted From minix in ubuntu or in an idle pc via pendrive. Has its own bootloader and kernel.

projects.title: Notes Application
projects.description: User Friendly Mobile Application used to Store Notes For Students, Demonstration UI/UX principles and CRUD operations in Firebase Database, Users can Save,Search, Delete, pin, filter their Comments.
